# ============================================================
# Avenzo Monorepo — Root environment reference
#
# This is a monorepo. Environment variables belong to each app:
#
#   apps/api            → apps/api/.env.example      (backend)
#   apps/customer-web   → apps/customer-web/.env.example
#   apps/restaurant-web → apps/restaurant-web/.env.example
#   apps/customer-mobile  → apps/customer-mobile/.env.example
#   apps/restaurant-mobile → apps/restaurant-mobile/.env.example
#
# NEVER commit real .env files to version control.
# Render: set env vars in the Render dashboard, not in a .env file.
# ============================================================
